close_reason: Added tests/integration/background-refresh-nonblocking.integration.spec.ts covering the instant-mutation search guarantee.
body: "## Context\nPR #87 shipped: detached worker + reindex lock for non-blocking search refresh (src/core/search/background-refresh.ts).\n\nUnit test: tests/unit/search-cache.spec.ts line 668 describes 'search background refresh'.\n\nThe background refresh uses a detached child process. No integration test verifies:\n1. create/update returns quickly (before reindex)\n2. a subsequent pm search eventually reflects the new item\n3. the reindex lock prevents duplicate workers\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- Integration test or expanded unit test that:\n  - Creates an item\n  - Verifies mutation returns promptly (not waiting for reindex)\n  - Polls or waits for reindex completion\n  - Verifies pm search can find the new item\n- OR: a documented reason why this is adequately covered by existing tests\n\n## Evidence\ntests/unit/search-cache.spec.ts line 668; src/core/search/background-refresh.ts; PR #87 session notes"
